				h2.bg-red.inline-block.padding-left-right-20 Getting Started
				p The Liger CSS Grid Framework has all the components initialized right out of the box. However, you can easily customize the grid to only include the necessary styles you want or need with Liger's <span class="code-div">@import</span> feature. 
				p When you open the liger.css file, you will notice the below list at the top of the css document. 
				.code 
